Installation:
download software_distribute from the master branch and copy to where you will run the code (SSD is fastest if available)
open terminal, cd to ../software_distribute/process_lm_sino/code
run the following commands: 
g++ process_lm_sino_superuser_CURRENT.cpp -o ../process_lm_sino
g++ scatter_lm_sino_tofinterp_CURRENT.cpp -o ../scatter_lm_sino_tof_local
g++ scatter_lm_sino_tofinterp_server_CURRENT.cpp -o ../scatter_lm_sino_tof_server

There are a few large files that are not hosted on github. These can be found on the BOX/LAB/ folder

